snippet.title: The Complex - An Interactive Movie | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Complex is an interactive sci-fi thriller movie from the publishing studio that brought you Five Dates, Maid of Sker, The Bunker and The Shapeshifting Detective. Out now on PC, PS4, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch. 

Visit on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1107790

After a major bio-weapon attack on London, two scientists find themselves in a locked-down laboratory with time, and air, running out. With interactive gameplay, your actions and your relationship with other characters will lead you to one of eight suspenseful endings.
